---
# Apollo Linux — Calamares module descriptor for apollo-desktop-select
type: "job"
name: "apollo-desktop-select"
interface: "python"
script: "main.py"
timeout: 600

# Reads apollo_desktop_chosen (or apollo_desktop_default) from GlobalStorage.
# Installs Apollo Desktop (openbox+apollo-shell+lightdm) or
# Hyprland (hyprland+ax-shell+sddm) into the target.
# Also configures GTK/Qt theming and environment variables.
